<emphasis id="749EE547FFB48800AE141CE6FE3DB027" box="[312,455,764,789]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Distribution</emphasis>
. Known only from the 
<typeStatus id="995187F7FFB48800ADF61CE6FCF7B024" box="[730,781,764,790]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">type</typeStatus>
locality in northern 
<collectingCountry id="3EFD79C5FFB48800ACD01CE6FB8FB024" box="[1020,1141,764,790]" name="Venezuela" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
near Caracas.
</paragraph>
